The Link’s Awakening amiibo is also my brothers, but the Links Awakening Game itself is mine since I preordered through GameStop last year (?).
I preordered a lot of games (sometime last year?) and they are going to be released over the next couple months. On a similar train of thought, I hope Animal Crossing has a special edition switch. I don’t have my own switch because I’ve been waiting but it’s ok I’ll keep playing on my bro’s. I am generally excited for the upcoming releases of Luigi Mansion and Pokémon~

Game Spyro ™ Reigneted Trilogy merupakan sebuah game yang dikembangkan oleh Toys for Bob dan diterbitkan oleh Activision. Spyro Reigneted Trilogy merupakan koleksi remaster dari 3 game pertama seri Spyro diantaranya Spyro The Dragon, Spyro 2 : Ripto's Rage! dan Spyro : Year of the Dragon.

Game ini mungkin sudah sangat dikenal oleh kalangan gamers, dimana awalnya game ini dirilis pada tahun 1998 untuk Playstation, namun saat ini versi remaster sudah hadir dengan membawa banyak pembaruan dengan masih menampilkan hiasan retro apik era Playstation 1. Game ini sudah dirilis pada tanggal 13 November 2018 untuk platform Playstation 4 dan Xbox One, sedangkan untuk Nintendo Switch dan PC (Steam) dirilis pada tanggal 3 September 2019 kemarin.

Selengkapnya 👇👇

We’re easing back into things to make sure the grind sticks this time. Routine, routine, routine... As you can see, I’ll be streaming at night going forward beginning tonight at 9:30pm (EST). Just like old times. 😏
.
I’m no longer going to have themed days anymore either and will just be streaming whatever I feel like playing that night. So if I feel like playing Smash, I’ll stream Smash, if I feel like playing Minecraft, I’ll be streaming Minecraft... you get the idea.

Smash is always the main focus so expect to see Ultimate for the most part when you tune in. I love streaming so I want to do everything I can so it doesn’t end up feeling like a chore everyday.
.

caption.text:
Das was für viele nicht von großer Bedeutung ist, ist für andere Menschen der größte Wunsch! 
Es liegt im Instinkt des Menschen immer besser werden zu wollen, sich mehr Besitz anschaffen zu wollen. Wir haben immer ein neues Ziel vor Augen. Da können wir nichts dran ändern und es ist auch gut so wie es ist! Denn sonst wäre die Menschheit noch lange nicht so weit wie jetzt.
Aber was viele dabei einfach vergessen ist: Dankbar zu sein! 
Dankbar für das was man hat. Für das was man bisher geschafft hat. Für das was man in diesem Augenblick erleben darf!
Wie oft habe ich gelesen, wie Reiseziele schlecht gemacht wurden, nur weil sie nicht rundherum so aussahen wie in den Reisemagazinen. Da waren Orte bei, wofür  manche Menschen Ihr halbes Leben lang sparen, nur um genau an diesem Fleck der Erde sein zu können. Um genau diese Stelle berühren zu können, dort atmen zu dürfen und mit eigenen Augen sehen zu können!
So oft hier habe ich gesehen, wie schnell hochwertige Sachen ersetzt wurden. Innerhalb kürzester Wochen. Dinge die sich andere Menschen schon jahrelang wünschen. Eine Schande ist das.
Egal ob Gesundheit, Familie, Besitz usw. Seid dankbar für das alles! 
Schätzt das was Ihr habt!!!
Morgen kann schon alles anders sein.
.

caption.text:
R.I.P. GameBoy Camera
Some of the best pictures you can take with the removed camera from Link’s Awakening.

#zelda #link #legendofzelda #nintendo #nintendoswitch #gameboy #gameboycolor #linksawakening #linksawakeningremake #koholint

Legend of Zelda: Link's Awakening is an incredible game who brings all the original functions of the 1993 game and adds more to the remake to make a new and modern experience of a memorable game.

Along with the graphical upgrades to the game, the return of the trendy game and fishing made me enjoy this game more than I would have ever thought. You can keep all your tools and weapons in the game whereas in the original you had to pick and choose what to bring with you.

With the introduction of fairy bottles, the game is made a bit easier in battle but to get these bottles aren't easy as you're not told where to find them.This is also the same for the heart pieces and seashells which if done, adds a bit extra to the closing scenes of the game.

A funny part for me would be Marin when she joins you. The trendy game and the well are two places to go to see her in action. Also you'll meet such characters as bootleg mario, kirby and Mr. Write (who I think is from animal crossing). Overall, this game has left you excited for the future of the Legend of Zelda and deserves a 9/10 on my list.

Evil Dead: A Fistful of Boomstick is an action hack and slash video game developed by VIS Entertainment and published by THQ. It was released for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox, and based on the movie trilogy The Evil Dead. It is set eleven years after the events of Army of Darkness, and three years after Jenny (Ash's girlfriend from Evil Dead: Hail to the King), was killed in a bus crash. Bruce Campbell returns to voice Ash, and the voices for supporting characters are provided by several notable voice actors, including Debi Mae West, Rob Paulsen and Tom Kenny. (Source @wikipedia)

caption.text:
젤다의 전설꿈꾸는 섬 엔딩 봤습니다~
모든 하트랑 모든 소라, 낚시, 비밀던전 포함 모든 던전, 던전 만들기 모든 과제, 자잘한 이벤트에 아이템도 죄다 수집하고 나서 진엔딩 봤습니다 ^^ 어릴적 흑백화면인 GB로 굉장히 재미있게 즐겼던 개임인데 옛날 추억을 떠올리며 향수에 젖어서 만족하면서 플레이 했습니다 ^^ 영상은 마지막던전인 성스러운 알 진입전에 바람 물고기의 노래로 입구 여는 오케스트라 입니다~ GB때도 그랬지만 개인적으로 저 부분이 이 꿈꾸는 섬에서 가장 마음이 드는 부분이네요~(링크는 오카리나 파지랑 운지 다시 배워야 할듯 하네요 ^^;;)
저 바람 물고기의 노래는 CF에서 안다인이라는 성우분이 한국어로 노래를 불러서 게임엔딩에 나오지 않을까 했는데 아쉽게도 나오지는 않더군요 ^^(닌텐도 스위치 코리아 홈페이지 가면 저 안다인님이 부른 보컬버전 음원 다운 받을 수 있습니다 ^^)
하여튼 어릴적 추억의 게임을 멋지게 리마스터 해줘서 또 그걸 너무 재미있게 즐겼던 것 같네요^^ 이제 마지막으로 어렵다는 하드모드로 처음부터 다시 시작해서 엔딩한번 더 보면 봉인해야 겠네요 ^^ #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬 #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬리메이크 #닌텐도스위치젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬 #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬한정판 #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬링크아미보 #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬아미보 #젤다의전설꿈꾸는섬한정판아트북 #엔딩 #바람물고기의노래 #THELEGENDOFZELDALinksAwakening #THELEGENDOFZELDA #ALinksAwakening #NS #NINTENDOSWITCH #닌텐도스위치 #NINTENDO #닌텐도 #게임 #GAME #취미

#nintendo #nintendoswitch #zelda #linksawakening #switch

The Legend of Zelda Fancast
————————————————————————
The Legend of Zelda is by far my favorite video game series out there. In addition to being amazing games, I think out of all the games in Nintendo’s catalogue, it would work the best being translated to film/tv as well. If that were ever to become a reality, I’d want the cast to look a little something like this:
•Ansel Elgort as Link
•Halston Sage as Princess Zelda
•Idris Elba as Ganondorf
•Gary Oldman as the King of Hyrule
•Tao Okamoto as Impa
•Kristen Bell as Navi
•Jack Black as Tingle
.
.
.
Hope you guys enjoy! Along with the main 3 characters, I decided to add the side characters that seem major/reoccurring across the series as a whole. If you guys are into this though, I might consider developing a plot and fuller cast! Don’t forget to follow @fn_fancaster for fancasts and other content!
